{%- doc -%}
  Intended for use in a block similar to the button block.

  @param {string} link - link to render
  @param {object} [block] - The block

  @example
  {% render 'button', link: '/collections/all' %}
{%- enddoc -%}

{% assign block_settings = block.settings %}
{% render 'button-custom-styles', block_settings: block_settings, block_id: block.id %}

<a
  {% if link == blank %}
    role="link"
    aria-disabled="true"
  {% else %}
    href="{{ link }}"
  {% endif %}
  class="
    size-style
    {{ block_settings.style_class }}
    {{ block_settings.style_class }}--{{ block.id }}
  "
  style="{% render 'size-style', settings: block_settings %}"
  {%- if block_settings.open_in_new_tab -%}
    target="_blank"
    rel="noopener noreferrer"
  {%- endif -%}
  {{ block.shopify_attributes }}
>
  {%- if block_settings.style_class == 'button-ghost' -%}
    <span class="button-ghost__label">{{ block_settings.label }}</span>
    <span class="svg-wrapper svg-wrapper--smaller button-ghost__icon" aria-hidden="true">
      {{- 'icon-caret.svg' | inline_asset_content -}}
    </span>
  {%- else -%}
    {{ block_settings.label }}
  {%- endif -%}
</a>

{%- comment -%}
  MOXIE: variante "Ghost" (fondo translúcido + blur + borde blanco) pedida por el Figma del
  hero (banner ppal) — ninguna de las clases nativas (.button/.button-secondary/.button-custom,
  ver assets/base.css) tiene backdrop-filter, así que se autocontiene acá en vez de tocar el
  archivo core. El ícono reutiliza assets/icon-caret.svg (mismo asset que
  snippets/slideshow-arrow.liquid), rotado -90deg para apuntar a la derecha.
{%- endcomment -%}
{% stylesheet %}
  .button-ghost {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    width: fit-content;
    margin-block: 0;
    padding-block: 8px;
    padding-inline: 16px;
    background-color: rgba(23, 23, 23, 0.1);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    backdrop-filter: blur(2px);
    border: 1px solid #ffffff;
    border-radius: 6px;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-decoration: none;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-paragraph--family);
    font-style: var(--font-paragraph--style);
    font-weight: var(--font-paragraph--weight);
    font-size: var(--font-paragraph--size);
    line-height: var(--font-paragraph--line-height);
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background-color var(--animation-speed) var(--animation-easing),
      border-color var(--animation-speed) var(--animation-easing);
  }

  .button-ghost:hover {
    background-color: rgba(23, 23, 23, 0.2);
  }

  .button-ghost[aria-disabled='true'] {
    opacity: 0.5;
    cursor: not-allowed;
  }

  .button-ghost__icon {
    color: currentcolor;
    rotate: -90deg;
  }
{% endstylesheet %}
